<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bg">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Потвърждение на поръчка</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #f8f5f2;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #40E0D0 0%, #5ee3d2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 10px 0 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.95;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .order-info {
            background: #f8f5f2;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .order-info-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e3de;
        }
        .order-info-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #666;
        }
        .value {
            color: #333;
        }
        .items-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .items-table thead {
            background: #40E0D0;
            color: white;
        }
        .items-table th {
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            font-weight: 600;
        }
        .items-table td {
            padding: 15px 12px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e8e3de;
        }
        .items-table tbody tr:last-child td {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .total-row {
            background: #f8f5f2;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .total-row td {
            padding: 20px 12px !important;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #333;
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #40E0D0;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #40E0D0;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>❤️ Bellamie</h1>
            <p>Ръчно изработени творения</p>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <p class="greeting">Здравейте, {{ order.user.email }}!</p>

            <p><strong>Благодарим Ви за Вашата поръчка!</strong></p>
            <p>Получихме Вашето запитване и ще се свържем с Вас скоро за потвърждение. Вашата поръчка е в състояние <strong>"Чакаща одобрение"</strong> и ще бъде обработена след нашето потвърждение.</p>

            <div class="order-info">
                <div class="order-info-row">
                    <span class="label">Номер на поръчка:</span>
                    <span class="value">#{{ order.id }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="order-info-row">
                    <span class="label">Дата:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ order.createdAt|date('d.m.Y H:i') }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="order-info-row">
                    <span class="label">Статус:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ order.status }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2 style="color: #333; margin-top: 30px;">Данни за доставка:</h2>

            <div class="order-info">
                <div class="order-info-row">
                    <span class="label">Име:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ customerData.fullName }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="order-info-row">
                    <span class="label">Телефон:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ customerData.phone }}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="order-info-row">
                    <span class="label">Адрес:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ customerData.address }}</span>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2 style="color: #333; margin-top: 30px;">Детайли на поръчката:</h2>

            <table class="items-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Продукт</th>
                        <th style="text-align: center;">Количество</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Цена</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Сума</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {% for item in order.items %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ item.product.name }}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: center;">{{ item.quantity }}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{ item.price }} лв</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{ item.subtotal|number_format(2, '.', '') }} лв</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                    <tr class="total-row">
                        <td colspan="3" style="text-align: right;">ОБЩО:</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{ order.totalPrice }} лв</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <p><strong>Важно:</strong> Това е автоматично потвърждение за получаване на заявката. След като разгледаме Вашата поръчка, ще получите допълнително съобщение за одобрение и следващите стъпки.</p>

            <center>
                <a href="http://localhost/" class="button">Посетете нашия магазин</a>
            </center>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Bellamie - Ръчно изработени творения</p>
            <p>
                <a href="http://localhost/">Начало</a> |
                <a href="mailto:asem4o@gmail.com">Контакти</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
